<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">tribhu</hi>vana<hi rend="grantha"> cakra</hi>vatti kOnErimEl koṇṭān Uṭai
<lb n="2" break="no"/>yār tirukkuṉṟākkuṭi Uṭaiya nāyaṉār kōyil tāṉattāṟku
<lb n="3"/>taṅkaḷ kōyil celitti mikiti Āka Iṟuttu pōtum
<lb n="4"/>poṉ nūṟum patiṉmūṉṟāvatu Etirāmāṇṭu paṅkuṉi mā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>tam mutal nāyaṉār tirukkuṉṟākkuṭi Uṭaiya nāyaṉāṟku
<lb n="6"/>nampērāl kaṭṭiṉa cuṉtara pāṇṭiyaṉ cantikku Amu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>tupaṭi cāttuppaṭi Uḷḷiṭṭa paṭi viyañcaṉattukkum Uṭalā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ka Ippoṉ nūṟum Iṟaiyili Ākat tantōm Ippaṭikku va
<lb n="9"/>riyilum kaḻikkaccoṉṉōm cantirātittavarai cella kal
<lb n="10" break="no"/>lilum cempilum veṭṭikkoṇṭu pūcai tāḻvaṟa naṭatta
<lb n="11"/>pōtuvatu <gap reason="lost" quantity="48" unit="character"/> 
</p>

